prompts.frontCover: Vibrant and dynamic comic book style birthday card front cover. The scene features two charming cartoon characters, a man and a woman, depicted in a highly exaggerated and funny action pose. The man is wearing a simple t-shirt and pants, with a look of comedic struggle and intense concentration as he playfully lifts the woman, who is dressed in a casual outfit. The woman is laughing joyfully, striking a heroic, triumphant superhero pose with one arm raised high in the air. The background is a classic comic book explosion, a "BOOM!" or "POW!" effect with radiating lines in bold, bright colors like electric yellow, fiery orange, and cyan blue. The entire composition has a flat 2D aesthetic with thick black outlines, Ben-Day dots for shading, and a saturated, high-contrast color palette typical of vintage comics. In the center of the composition, integrated into the design, is the text "HAPPY BIRTHDAY, LAO LAO!" written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, possibly with a subtle drop shadow to make it pop. The overall feeling is energetic, hilarious, and full of love.
